{"tid":740550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[齊鼓掌]四川工業區科技公司爆炸 最少19死12傷","createTime":"2018-07-13T03:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T04:26:22.000Z","uid":14208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4086ed8f3849176cb9ca28d0501136ba9b5f4a","tid":740550,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"四川工業區科技公司爆炸 最少19死12傷<br />\n<br />\n四川宜賓市江安縣陽春工業園區內發生爆炸和火警，至少19人死亡，12人受傷，沒有生命危險。省市領導及相關部門負責人已到場了解情況。事故原因有待調查。<br />\n      <br />\n      事發昨日傍晚6時半，位於陽春工業園區內的宜賓恒達科技有限公司發生爆炸。網上流傳爆炸一刻後片段，可見工廠內火光熊熊，濃煙沖天。消防接報到場撲救，現場火勢已被撲熄，搜救工作亦已結束。當地政府正進行善後工作。<br />\n      <br />\n      四川省委書記彭清華要求積極搶救傷者、做好善後工作，同時盡快查明事故原因，依法依規嚴肅追責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=e&amp;nid=157129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3De%26nid%3D157129&d=3NWyfr1RrCcTnPgagDBXZG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c374a22e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3De%26nid%3D157129&h=677ae5bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=e&amp;nid=157129</a>"},{"pid":"d48f9507efaebc5b76239828ab7548952c0507d6","tid":740550,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/112901_d444c4494abec77b9a1f99a6ce5abc18.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F112901_d444c4494abec77b9a1f99a6ce5abc18.gif&h=648c4636&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08fd21df73cec06efd2002ec7500803338a736f4","tid":740550,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27780ea7b5474c8fa2dec7a2b47f35ac850e211f","tid":740550,"uid":175645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"水浸完又爆炸<br />\n贏国俾四川放鬆下la"},{"pid":"59e82c148265b69c79847b891371e5ac372846ef","tid":740550,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:19:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亮劍</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a7a0110820634f7017fdf1780b9e5ebe62378bce","tid":740550,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59e82c148265b69c79847b891371e5ac372846ef","tid":740550,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:19:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亮劍</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"自爆都算係一種攻擊手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f736883c85fe4e85d0af5b81f6cc9a9a54350c","tid":740550,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}